data.description: Have you wanted to own a beautiful, split foyer home with endless possibilities and your own private pool and fenced in yard? Then look no further! As you enter this recently painted, spectacular home, going up the stairs to your right will be 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Straight ahead is a gorgeous updated kitchen with a stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher, and gas range with a large bi-folding, two door pantry. Continuing through the kitchen, you will circle around through a dining area and into your spacious living room. Out the back door, there is a cozy sunroom that leads you down the stairs to your pool surrounded by a wooden fence for privacy. The large back yard is completely enclosed by a chain-link fence. Sit out in your lawn chair or in your sunroom and enjoy the stunning wildlife that visits. This home is a must see!
